Add blades to the inventory.

Usage:
  cani add blade [flags]

Flags:
  -C, --cabinet int            Cabinet ID (default 1000)
  -c, --chassis int            Chassis ID
  -h, --help                   help for blade
  -v, --hmn-vlan int           HMN VLAN ID
  -l, --list-supported-types   List supported hardware types.
  -p, --port int               Switchport
  -R, --role string            Role
  -s, --slot int               Slot ID
  -r, --sub-role string        Sub-role
  -t, --type string            Hardware type.  Allowed values: []

Global Flags:
      --config string   Path to the configuration file
  -D, --debug           additional debug output
  -S, --simulation      Use simulation mode for hsm-simulation-environment
